ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
Subject2004-2005 - Transfer Undistributed Balances ** wheat, amber durum wheat, barley and designated barley **
PrecisOrder authorizing the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD (a) to adjust its accounts as of December 31, 2011, by transferring the undistributed funds in the 2004-05 pool account for wheat, amber durum wheat, barley and designated barley to a separate account; and (b) to pay to the persons who are entitled to receive payments the amount to which they are entitled out of the separate account.
